ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 176 - (Ontario) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 176 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes financial assistance to the province of ONTARIO with respect to the ICE STORM which caused extended power outages and extensive damage to private property, small businesses, and to provincial and municipal infrastructure, and affected several communities in the southern, central and eastern regions of the province from December 21 to 22, 2013.
